          "reviewBody": "Dear Parents,\nPlease consider this as a very genuine review and a very honest one. Ryan Internation school, NOIDA is  not a place where you should admit your kids. If you want to ruin there school life you can choose this school. The New Principal is of no use and just want money. Specially class 10th, 11th, 12th Teachers they are playing with kids education. Ego of teachers is aboce everything. A child who makes principals drawing and isa below average child will get admission in PCM in 11th but a honest student scoring 60-70% will not get the admission as per the norms because he is not the \"chamcha\" of so called egoistic teachers. Teachers dont check the papers correctly 9just because of the ego and attitude. I really dont want to name any teacher but Teachers teaching MATHS in class 10th RYAN NOIDA are someone who should work on there behaviour towards students. They should understand they are doing wrong and its high time they should understand. Its not just about my kid, I will admit him in a much better school than RYAN if required. But honestly parents please consider this before you admit your kid in the school.",
